SPLAT PERL MODULE
VERSION 0.01

This README (as opposed to README.md) is for CPAN so that people
browsing the archive can use it to get an idea of what the SPLAT
module is about. 

STANDARD PERL MODULE INSTRUCTIONS FOLLOW:

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc SPLAT

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=SPLAT

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/SPLAT

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/SPLAT

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/SPLAT/


